### Valid request with token
GET http://localhost:5016/api/users
Authorization: Bearer valid-token

### Invalid token
GET http://localhost:5016/api/users
Authorization: Bearer wrong-token

### Missing token
GET http://localhost:5016/api/users

### Trigger error (non-existent user)
GET http://localhost:5016/api/users/999
Authorization: Bearer valid-token

### Create user (valid)
POST http://localhost:5016/api/users
Authorization: Bearer valid-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ada",
  "email": "ada@techhive.com",
  "password": "securePass123"
}
